  "band_name": "Talkhouse",
  "bio": [
    {
      "value": "Blending head-slamming highs and tear-jerking lows, TALKHOUSE offers carefully crafted lyrics, melodies, and riffs for listeners who enjoy complexity but still know when to let go and just have fun."
    },
    {
      "value": "A product of New York, TALKHOUSE has been tearing up stages like Arlene's Grocery, selling out the Bitter End, headlining Mercury Lounge and more."
    },
    {
      "value": "Stay tuned for their debut single Downtown, releasing Friday, May 8th."
    }
